        <h3><a href="/questions/19371850/sunspot-search-multiple-models-using-a-conditional-with-call" class="question-hyperlink">Sunspot - Search multiple models using a conditional with call</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            class Cat &lt; ActiveRecord::Base
  searchable do
    string :color
  end
end
class Dog &lt; ActiveRecord::Base
  searchable do
    string :color
  end
end


Given the models Cat and Dog above, how do ...
